text: The Mullsjö Pentecostal Church () is a church building in Mullsjö, Sweden. It belongs to the Swedish Pentecostal Movement. The current building was opened in 1964. It was rebuilt to its current look in 1984. ==References== ==Other websites== *Mullsjö-Nyhem Pentecostal Congregation Category:Churches in Sweden Category:Mullsjö
